column5: Pretty cool Web Cam of the Famous Abbey Road Crossing! Hilarious during the day with tourists.. http://www.abbeyroad.com/visit/
lol, i watched it for 2 minutes just now, and saw 4 different ppl do "the wakl" across the crossing. haha  funny how an lp cover makes an intersection famous. lol.
HAHAHAH that is awesome....people are actually blocking traffic to take a picture doing THE WALK
